Cell["", "ExampleDelimiter",ExpressionUUID->"65ad973d-1ba7-4cf1-9b07-0a65ea6cf06d"],

Cell["\<\
A rogue's gallery: the 21 hard unknot diagrams catalogued by B. A. Burton, \
H.-C. Chang, M. L\[ODoubleDot]ffler, A. de Mesmay, C. Maria, S. Schleimer, E. \
Sedgwick and J. Spreer, \"Hard Diagrams of the Unknot\", Experimental \
Mathematics 33(3), 2023 (arXiv:2104.14076). These diagrams defeat naive \
Reidemeister simplification -- several provably require extra crossings \
before they can be simplified at all. The diagrams ship with this paclet as \
example data. In order of crossing number (9 to 141), with the names and \
attributions used in that paper:\
\>", "ExampleText",ExpressionUUID->"6ca37fad-4732-49a5-9fd7-064ced22effb"],

